metadata.name: REACH
metadata.description:
REACH is a piece from PARTS UNKNOWN. The project is a journey of rebirth and growth. It is the idea, and feeling, of warm liquid hugging the contours of a body. A darkened backdrop intertwined with colorful, saturated, bright, and wet highlights. Micro details give the viewer the sense of movement and motion.

2000 x 2000 pixels

Created by Bryan Coleman December 2021

Bryan Coleman is an American digital artist with a degree in time based media. Bryan has worked with companies across the globe and he focuses on the creation of an idea for a wide range of projects.
